{"tid":1282633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分析一下：網絡陰謀論","createTime":"2019-07-03T15:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T16:12:25.000Z","uid":271774,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e89adc06bcfe1ee94d4762653d8b87be28de8cbb","tid":1282633,"uid":271774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"事先聲明，如有講錯，可以補充一下<br />\n有朋友同我講whatsapp+FB兩個都gg左。加上尋日ddos單野，忽發其想。<br />\n兩次網絡攻擊：<br />\n（１） 主流媒體　　　（２） 通訊軟件<br />\n尋晚ddos影響既大部分都係用開既網站，而兩次既攻擊時間都係<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夜晚</span></span><br />\n考慮到777係四點鐘衝出黎開記招，目的係去<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">混淆國際消息</span></span><br />\n所以果日777既英文同中文回應都係唔一樣（有人話英文答得特別長）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今晚針對既係圖片同音頻，呢兩樣野其實可以有<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">（1）做證明(有圖有真相)</span></strong>; 同 <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">（2）短時間傳遞消息</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尋晚有巴打係連仔share左一段有關於台灣明居正教授分析香港六月事件既片（縮減版）<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJBeGrBCNus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJJBeGrBCNus&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=1e850786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJBeGrBCNus</a><br />\n教授有提到一毛開始出動，同埋中共擔心香港既示威會蔓延到大陸<br />\n當然，係完整版入面，明教授有提出客觀，但對香港人黎講會好灰既意見，大家睇完當有個知字就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結合以上考慮，我有以下既問題／結論：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 證明國際聲音對中共有必定既影響力，影響上面決策，所以呢幾日政府風向轉去影響本土同外媒既聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n2. 連續兩日既網絡攻擊，可能係上面測試緊有咩方法，用防火牆／其他方法，將香港消息封鎖番係境內，拖慢外國對香港局勢既反應<br />\n<br />\n3. 政府意識到洗白警察＋建制聲音已經未必能夠平息到民憤，所以網絡攻擊可以幫手減弱宣傳既效果<br />\n<br />\n4. 政府知道有活動既時候，大家普遍用乜野方式溝通，呢兩日都可以當做佢地嘗試去阻止／搵方法將大家斷開聯絡<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n可能我講到1999咁，因為我都係一邊諗一邊打，如果有講錯就改正同幫手解釋番<br />\n感謝！！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e625eb609edaff1903b4bee879d4728324626a92","tid":1282633,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"(與本文無關) 大家記得善用Blockchain backup重要資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【網絡安全】如何匿名免費咁放資料上Ethereum Blockchain測試網絡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282498</a>"},{"pid":"e3fa53283bb5914f47f6e5139af65c5d4b2d8ea7","tid":1282633,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"ec466d3346c1894a3946f9c1385ced047a04b3b5","tid":1282633,"uid":271774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"同埋有社工朋友有同我解釋<br />\n佢啲仔以為Whatsapp del哂d msg警察就搵唔到記錄<br />\n但事實上，警察係有方法睇番＋留底你既whatsapp 記錄<br />\n所以大家用番TG可能會好啲(雖然未必有用)"},{"pid":"d0353f58046e667b7028f4ba51ef301e9ec61f70","tid":1282633,"uid":271774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76a8175da2a7dbb0576284b8decaaefc27c78e14","tid":1282633,"uid":271774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:30:02.000Z","msg":"大家係咪都已經訓著哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803e9e744ce430079ccf9393233f47ba5df509ec","tid":1282633,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"見到p牌五毛冇晒"},{"pid":"f8f1ad60ec945bbf27457a9de0472e064f598a5a","tid":1282633,"uid":271774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"506d8ea6589b045dd3f74bff8643df66c0f78347","tid":1282633,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"32f82b89939915265ada84ea61d7eebc81810b95","tid":128